comments: McDaniels (MIN) makes contact with Gobert's (UTA) arm that affects his shot near the rim.
Bogdanovic (UTA) makes marginal contact to the arm of Russell (MIN) at the end of the drive.
Russell (UTA) deflects the ball to save it from going out of bounds and once he reestablishes himself in bounds, he legally starts his dribble.
Gobert (UTA) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Russell (MIN) firms up delivers legal contact while setting the pick.
O'Neale (UTA) makes contact to Edwards' (MIN) arm after his gather and a shooting foul should have been assessed.
O'Neale (UTA) reaches in and marginal contact occurs with Rubio (MIN) after he releases the pass.
Bogdanovic (UTA) commits a take foul on Towns (MIN).
Clarkson (UTA) commits a take foul on Russell (MIN).
Clarkson (UTA) commits a take foul on Okogie (MIN).
